<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Delete Your Likemind Account</h1>
        <div class="app-name">Likemind - Account Deletion Request</div>

        <section>
            <p>
                If you wish to delete your Likemind account and associated data, please follow the steps below. 
                This process is permanent and cannot be undone.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    <span class="step-number">1</span>
                    <strong>Open the Likemind app</strong> on your device and log in to your account.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="step-number">2</span>
                    Navigate to your <strong>Profile</strong> page (tap your profile icon in the top right corner).
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="step-number">3</span>
                    Scroll down and tap on <strong>"Settings"</strong> or look for the account deletion option.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="step-number">4</span>
                    Select <strong>"Delete Account"</strong> and confirm your decision.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="step-number">5</span>
                    Alternatively, you can send an email deletion request (see below).
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Email Deletion Request</h2>
            <p>
                If you cannot access the app or prefer to request deletion via email, please send a request to:
            </p>
            <div class="contact-box">
                <p>
                    <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:benediktlangenberger@gmail.com?subject=Account Deletion Request">benediktlangenberger@gmail.com</a><br>
                    <strong>Subject:</strong> Account Deletion Request<br>
                    <strong>Include:</strong> Your email address associated with your Likemind account
                </p>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                We will process your deletion request within 30 days of receipt.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Data That Will Be Deleted</h2>
            <p>When you delete your account, the following data will be permanently removed:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email address, password, authentication tokens</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Data:</strong> Display name, birthdate, slogan, interests</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Photos:</strong> All uploaded photos and images</li>
                <li><strong>Questionnaire Answers:</strong> All compatibility questionnaire responses</li>
                <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> Stored latitude and longitude coordinates</li>
                <li><strong>Messages:</strong> All sent and received messages in conversations</li>
                <li><strong>Matches:</strong> All match records and compatibility scores</li>
                <li><strong>Conversations:</strong> All chat conversations and message history</li>
                <li><strong>User Preferences:</strong> App settings and preferences</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Data Retention and Exceptions</h2>
            <p>
                <strong>Retention Period:</strong> Account deletion requests are processed within 30 days. 
                After processing, all associated data will be permanently deleted from our servers.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                <strong>Data That May Be Retained:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may retain certain data if required by law, 
                    such as for tax purposes, legal disputes, or regulatory compliance. This data will 
                    be retained only for the minimum period required by applicable law.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Anonymized Analytics:</strong> Aggregated, anonymized data that cannot be 
                    linked to your identity may be retained for analytics and service improvement purposes.
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Backup Systems:</strong> Data may exist in backup systems for up to 90 days 
                    after deletion, after which it will be permanently removed.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>What Happens After Deletion</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>You will no longer be able to log in to your Likemind account</li>
                <li>All your profile information will be removed from other users' views</li>
                <li>Your messages will be deleted from conversations</li>
                <li>You will be removed from other users' match lists</li>
                <li>You can create a new account using the same email address after deletion</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <p>
                <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. 
                Please ensure you have saved any important information before proceeding. 
                Once your account is deleted, you will lose access to all your data, matches, and conversations.
            </p>
        </div>

